{"type": "article", "id": 29568, "title": "相机背带", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-13T23:08:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 69, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160713175437PVreoaHtE7duRYSn.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>我们都希望在旅行时记录下那些特别的瞬间，然而扛着沉重的相机很容易对颈椎和肩膀造成损伤。为了缓解相机对身体的重压，美国 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PONTEleatherco/\" rel=\"nofollow\">PONTE Leather</a> 公司专门设计了一款名为 Life-Strap 的背带。它在后颈处附有一个额外的扣环，能够与背包的提手相连，让受力面更均匀地分布在后背。背带自适应的设计可以用于任何相机，哪怕是古董机也能够利用特制的金属环进行调节。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ponteleather/camera-lift-strap-explore-and-capture-comfortably\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，帆布款和皮革款的最低价分别为 26 和 59 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713175457n1XPGUIVRNuf639v.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713175457KhyQNDo2sCF3g7ZW.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677467\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713175457AMIiX2aOnEyKxfwe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607131754575prR6gkISFTc8bWA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}